title: i cant get alistar skin plz help
body:
Attempting to use the link to redeem the unchained Alistar only brings up a blank page.
I have subscribed to the YouTube channel.
But am unable to discover how to get skin through normal means.
Please see the attached screenshot where I am signed in and subscribed to RiotGamesInc YouTube channel. And the second page where the http://youtube.na.leagueoflegends.com... brings up a blank page.
If unchained Alistar is no longer available I understand, and this ticket can be disregarded after I am notified of such. Otherwise can someone please direct me on how to resolve this issue?
Thank you,
my name is stephanbay666

replies.body: No worries, we can help!  Hit us up in a [support ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) and we'll see what we can do for you individually through there!
